<body>
The visualization2d package is separated in animation and engine subpackages.
All classes in the animation subpackages extends from desmoj classes. 
The engine subpackage contains a 2d animation engine.<br>
The communication between both parts runs about a cmds-file. While the simulation runs, 
the classes in animation subpackage write commands in the cmds-file. Afterwards, 
for animation, this file is read by a viewer class in engine subpackage.
